            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>This error isn‚Äôt specific to Redash. Have you tried Googling it? There appears to be a solution <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/72695311/failure-starting-docker-container-failed-to-create-shim-task-oci-runtime-crea">here</a> that involves modifying the Dockerfile. It would be helpful to know what other debugging steps you‚Äôve tried.</p>
