            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>yes you‚Äôre right the problem is specific to docker when running in a lxc container<br>
the first solution which works is to create a KVM virtual machine in proxmox‚Ä¶ so the VM is better isolated from the host an docker runs successfully<br>
but I will let you know if I find the good docker configuration with a LXC container<br>
bye thanks<br>
Maurice</p>
